(129, 1, '2014-10-22 06:55:29', '2014-10-22 06:55:29', 'We do everything within our capacity to reduce our impact by using recyclable packaging and sourcing our products from environmentally aware companies. In our pursuit to become an ethical organization we endeavor to ensure the following principles are maintained in our company.\r\n\r\n- To ensure that our products are being sourced from safe facilities, by workers who are treated fairly and paid adequately.\r\n- To ensure that all our products are free from: Phthalate, Phosphate, Paraben, and Sulfate.\r\n- To ensure that our products are vegan-friendly, by explicitly refraining from the act of animal testing on any of our products.\r\n- To protect the environment as much as possible by practicing the 3 ‘R’ system: Recycle, Reuse, and Reduce; by using sustainable packaging for all of our products.\r\n- To ensure that we use recycled or recyclable materials such as: Glass and PET, to deplete unnecessary wastage to our environment.', 'Ethical Sourcing', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ethical-sourcing', '', '', '2014-10-27 07:22:55', '2014-10-27 07:22:55', '', 0, 'http://117.3.103.72:8080/?page_id=129', 0, 'page', '', 0),
