(131, 1, '2014-10-22 06:56:30', '2014-10-22 06:56:30', '<div><a href="http://117.3.103.72:8080/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/bottle-in-box.jpg"><img class="img-responsive alignnone size-medium wp-image-241" src="http://117.3.103.72:8080/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/bottle-in-box-300x199.jpg" alt="Our packaging" width="300" height="199" /></a></div>\r\nWrapped in an overt design of Matt-Black extravagance, our packaging is a leap from the old fashionedcommercial packaging commonly found on the high street. Our boxes are uniquely hand crafted from the finest paper, which opens up to reveal a hand pleated satin lined interior.\r\n\r\nThe striking ‘Signature’ Logo modestly glides across the box, reflecting the extrovercy and uniqueness of our perfumes.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, as ‘reusable’ is a fundamental part of our environmental undertaking, our boxes can be used as a accessory to store your most precious luxuries.', 'Our Packaging', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'packaging', '', '', '2014-10-31 09:33:19', '2014-10-31 09:33:19', '', 0, 'http://117.3.103.72:8080/?page_id=131', 0, 'page', '', 0),
