(257, 1, '2014-11-03 13:22:48', '2014-11-03 13:22:48', 'AMBIGIOUS\n\nSPICY, FRESH, WARM, PUNGENT, COMPLEX\n\nFruits, flowers, and woods are the ingredients that make up Odd Rush. This fragrance represents the natural essences that glide through our noses. The infusion of fresh fruity notes and the sumptuous bouquet of floral notes leave you yearning to dab some more.\n\nNotes\n\nTop: Peach, Apricot, Black Currant, Raspberry, Mango, Coconut, Bergamot\n\nHeart: Mandarin Orange, Carnation, Cinnamon, Jasmine, Geranium, Lily of the valley\n\nBase: Vanilla, Benzoin, Tonka Bean, Amber, Musk, Patchouli, Sandalwood\n\nMood: Classical\n\n0.4 FL. OZ./OZ. LIQ/12 ML', 'ODD RUSH', '<p>Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nisl ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p>\n<p>Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla facilisi.</p>\n', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '220-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-03 13:22:48', '2014-11-03 13:22:48', '', 220, 'http://117.3.103.72:8080/220-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(258, 1, '2014-11-03 13:28:38', '2014-11-03 13:28:38', '<header id="page-heading">\r\n<h1>ABOUT US</h1>\r\n</header><article class="full-width clearfix">\r\n<div class="entry clearfix">\r\n\r\nSignature Fragrances London™ was founded by two friends from London. Having an earnest passion for all things perfumed, the pair decided to actualize their strong passion for perfumery by introducing a diverse range of fragrances that everybody would enjoy.\r\n<h2>OUR PERFUMES</h2>\r\nThe belief at Signature Fragrances London™ is that ‘your perfume has the right to be smelt by others’. Our perfumes are categorized by four of the most popular fragrance families in the world. Each fragrance carries its own identity that adds to the complexity and pungency of each blend, giving its user a unique sensory experience.\r\n\r\nOur perfumes are at an indulgent Pure Parfum strength – the highest form of perfume, this improves the length of the perfume and leads to a more longer lasting scent perfect for today’s hectic lifestyles, revealing gradually from dawn to dusk. Diverging from the norm of Eau de parfum and Eau de toilette, Signature Fragrances London™ has quickly gained credit for rekindling the art of pure perfume and offering uncontested value by providing perfumes that contain little or no alcohol.\r\n\r\nEach collection has been hand selected to produce a trilogy of fragrances that offer a personal connection between the perfumer and buyer, with emphasis placed firmly on the quality of ingredients rather than the quantity. With other brands focusing on advertising and increased sales, Signature Fragrances London™ seeks to bring the true essence of perfumery back to the 21st century, seeking an exploration of unique blends sourced from around the world.\r\n\r\nSignature Fragrances™ aims to offer our Signateers™ the experience to explore the uniqueness and diversity of scent, and to ensure that we continue to fascinate you by offering extraordinary fragrances that restore your personal identity.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article>', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-03 13:28:38', '2014-11-03 13:28:38', '', 33, 'http://117.3.103.72:8080/33-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
