(264, 1, '2014-11-04 07:38:48', '2014-11-04 07:38:48', 'We will only order to the address given. All orders require a signature upon receipt of delivery, if you are not present to sign for your order, the courier will leave a card for you to make alternative arrangements.\r\n\r\nWe are unable to process orders to a P. O Box address.\r\n\r\nIf you encounter any problems when ordering then please contact us on 0208 345 9392 (Lines are open between 09:00 – 17: 00pm) or alternatively email: sales@signaturefragrances.co.uk\r\n\r\nONLINE RETURN POLICY\r\n\r\nCan I return my order?\r\nYes, if for any reason you are not entirely satisfied, or you receive a faulty item then you may return any item in its original condition for a full refund within 14 days from delivery.\r\n(Signature Fragrances™ will not accept any item that has been used or damaged)\r\nEmail: sales@signaturefragrances.co.uk to discuss your query.\r\n\r\nHow do I return my order?\r\n\r\nSimply package up your purchase with the order note, and send it to the address below. Please remember to ask for a proof of postage.\r\n\r\nSignature Fragrances Online\r\nPlot 5 Lockwood House,\r\nKennington Oval,\r\nLondon\r\nSE11 5SZ\r\n\r\n*UK only\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNon UK customer\r\n\r\nIf you are not a UK customer, you are welcome to return your items by emailing: sales@signaturefragrances.co.uk and someone from our dedicated team will respond to your enquiry.\r\n\r\nWhen will I receive my return?\r\n\r\nReturns are usually processed within 2 -3 days of us receiving the items back. Please allow up to a week for refunds to show on your account. We will refund you by the same method of payment (i.e. same card, PayPal)\r\n\r\nWhen will I receive my exchange?\r\n\r\nExchanges are usually processed and dispatched within 2-3 days of us receiving the goods back.\r\n\r\nWe can only exchange an item for a different perfume or size, providing it is of the same value as the original item or lower. In the case of the latter, we will refund you the difference.', 'DELIVERY & RETURNS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'delivery-returns', '', '', '2014-11-04 07:38:48', '2014-11-04 07:38:48', '', 0, 'http://117.3.103.72:8080/?page_id=264', 0, 'page', '', 0),
