(301, 1, '2014-11-10 19:44:56', '2014-11-10 19:44:56', '<div class="entry clearfix">Signature Fragrances London™ was founded by two friends from London. Having an earnest passion for all things perfumed, the pair decided to actualize their strong passion for perfumery by introducing a diverse range of fragrances that everybody would enjoy.\n<h2>OUR PERFUMES</h2>\nThe belief at Signature Fragrances London™ is that ‘your perfume has the right to be smelt by others’. Our perfumes are categorized by four of the most popular fragrance families in the world. Each fragrance carries its own identity that adds to the complexity and pungency of each blend, giving its user a unique sensory experience.\n\nOur perfumes are at an indulgent Pure Parfum strength – the highest form of perfume, this improves the length of the perfume and leads to a much more longer lasting scent; perfect for today’s hectic lifestyles, revealing itself gradually from dawn to dusk. Diverging from the norm of Eau de parfum and Eau de toilettes, Signature Fragrances London has quickly gained credit for rekindling the art of pure perfume and offering uncontested value by providing perfume oils that contain little or no alcohol.\n\nEach collection has been hand selected to produce a trilogy of fragrances that offer a personal connection between the perfumer and buyer, with emphasis placed firmly on the quality of ingredients rather than the quantity. With other brands focusing on advertising and increased sales, Signature Fragrances London™ seeks to bring the true essence of perfumery back to the 21st century, seeking an exploration of unique blends sourced from around the world.\n\nSignature Fragrances™ aims to offer our Signateers™ the experience to explore the uniqueness and diversity of scent, and to ensure that we continue to fascinate you by offering extraordinary fragrances that restore your personal identity.\n\n</div>', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-10 19:44:56', '2014-11-10 19:44:56', '', 33, 'http://117.3.103.72:8080/33-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(302, 1, '2014-11-10 19:45:37', '2014-11-10 19:45:37', '<div class="entry clearfix">Signature Fragrances London™ was founded by two friends from London. Having an earnest passion for all things perfumed, the pair decided to actualize their strong passion for perfumery by introducing a diverse range of fragrances that everybody would enjoy.\r\n<h2>OUR PERFUMES</h2>\r\nThe belief at Signature Fragrances London™ is that ‘your perfume has the right to be smelt by others’. Our perfumes are categorized by four of the most popular fragrance families in the world. Each fragrance carries its own identity that adds to the complexity and pungency of each blend, giving its user a unique sensory experience.\r\n\r\nOur perfumes are at an indulgent Pure Parfum strength – the highest form of perfume, this improves the length of the perfume and leads to a much more longer lasting scent; perfect for today’s hectic lifestyles, revealing itself gradually from dawn to dusk. Diverging from the norm of Eau de parfum and Eau de toilettes, Signature Fragrances London has quickly gained credit for rekindling the art of pure perfume and offering uncontested value by providing perfume oils that contain little or no alcohol.\r\n\r\nEach collection has been hand selected to produce a trilogy of fragrances that offer a personal connection between the perfumer and buyer, with emphasis placed firmly on the quality of ingredients rather than the quantity. With other brands focusing on advertising and increased sales, Signature Fragrances London™ seeks to bring the true essence of perfumery back to the 21st century, seeking an exploration of unique blends sourced from around the world.\r\n\r\nSignature Fragrances aims to offer Signateers the experience to explore the uniqueness and diversity of scent, and to ensure that we continue to fascinate you by offering extraordinary fragrances that restore your personal identity.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-v1',