(9, 9, 'nav_menu', '', 0, 0),
(10, 10, 'product_cat', 'The men’s collection\r\nCommunicates the example of the modern man; clean, ambitious, and outgoing who knows that smelling good is part of feeling good. Popular combinations, which yield strong parts of the human sensory experience, can be found in these ‘very’ masculine fragrances. ', 11, 5),
(11, 11, 'product_cat', '', 0, 0),
(12, 12, 'nav_menu', '', 0, 17),
(13, 13, 'product_cat', 'The Oud Collection\r\nThe quintessence of all noble raw materials, the Oud Collection provides a platform for those seeking exclusivity and uniqueness. Once proclaimed as ‘the liquid gold’, this material known as Agarwood sets the trend for all things excessive and rich.', 11, 1),
(14, 14, 'product_cat', '', 0, 0),
(15, 15, 'product_cat', 'The Oriental Collection\r\nexplores the richness and nostalgia of the Far East. Each perfume has been carefully selected to reflect the complex blends that come from this divine region; from the spices in India to the rare Agarwood in Cambodia, these fragrances create a harmonious link of exotic trilogy.', 11, 3),
(16, 16, 'product_cat', 'The Floral Collection \r\nsets the tone for everything fresh, sophisticated, and heavenly. Essence extracts from different flowers such as Jasmine, Rose, and violet provide a provocative composition \r\nused to form the fragrances in this category.', 11, 5),
(17, 17, 'product_cat', 'The Sweet Collection\r\nA trip down memory lane takes us back to our carefree attitude where everything was sweet and spontaneous. The sweet collection harmonises an extraordinary array of blends that start off sweet, but end with miraculous transformation to sophistication and class.', 11, 3),
(18, 18, 'product_cat', 'The Fresh Collection \r\ninvokes notes from classic extracts. A knockout array of sumptuous blends coated together to produce a clean and cooling scent that evokes a sense of no-nonsense attitude.', 11, 3),
(19, 19, 'product_cat', 'The Women’s Collection \r\nIncludes fresh and rejuvenating scents which play coy with dessert-like top notes and the flirtation of flowers. These fragrances appeal to a real women, an individual who is bold and confident.', 11, 3),
(20, 20, 'product_cat', '', 0, 2);
